{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-060","title":"Sentence 60","sectionId":"sentences-051","sectionTitle":"Sentence 51-60","pageStart":392,"pageEnd":397,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":17,"duplicateEntryCount":20,"pages":[{"number":392,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 60"},{"type":"text","text":"But as more and more accumulations of strata were cataloged in"},{"type":"text","text":"more and more places, it became clear that the sequences of rocks"},{"type":"text","text":"sometimes differed from region to region and that no rock type was ever"},{"type":"text","text":"going to become a reliable time marker throughout the world."},{"type":"text","text":"由于在越来越多的地方，越来越多的岩层积累形式被编入分"},{"type":"text","text":"类，以下信息变得清晰了：岩层顺序有时因地区的不同而不同，全"},{"type":"text","text":"世界没有一种特定的岩层能被认作是可靠的时间标志。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是“It became clear that ... and that ...”。其中两个that分别"},{"type":"text","text":"引导一个主语从句，作本句真正的主语：that the sequences differed from"},{"type":"text","text":"region to region and that no rock type was going to become a time marker"},{"type":"text","text":"throughout the world。句首的as引导一个原因状语从句。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"catalog /ˈkætəlɔːɡ/ n. 目录 vt. 登记；为…编目","headword":"catalog"}]},{"number":393,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"记忆 cata（下面）+log（说话）→（列出）在下面要说的话→目"},{"type":"text","text":"录"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 register v. 登记，为…编目录"},{"type":"entry","text":"sequence /ˈsiːkwəns/ n. 连续；顺序","headword":"sequence"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 sequ（跟随）+ence→顺序"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 sequential a. 按次序的，顺序的"},{"type":"text","text":"sequent a. 连续的"},{"type":"text","text":"subsequent a. 随后的，后来的"},{"type":"entry","text":"marker /ˈmɑːrkər/ n. 标识，标志","headword":"marker"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 marked a. 显著的；有记号的"},{"type":"text","text":"markedly ad. 显著地，明显地"},{"type":"text","text":"throughout /θruːˈaʊt/ prep. 遍及"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"}]},{"number":394,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"常见地质词汇："},{"type":"entry","text":"volcano /vɑːlˈkeɪnoʊ/ n. 火山","headword":"volcano"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 volcanic a. 火山的"},{"type":"text","text":"active volcano 活火山"},{"type":"text","text":"shield volcano 盾状火山"},{"type":"text","text":"cone volcano 锥状火山"},{"type":"text","text":"extinct volcano 死火山"}]},{"number":395,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"dormant /ˈdɔːrmənt/ a. 静止的；休眠的","headword":"dormant"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 dormant volcano 休眠火山"},{"type":"text","text":"volcanic ash 火山灰"},{"type":"text","text":"volcanic dust 火山尘"},{"type":"entry","text":"eject /iˈdʒekt/ v. 喷出","headword":"eject"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 reject vt. 拒绝"},{"type":"text","text":"object v. 反对"},{"type":"text","text":"inject vt. 注射"},{"type":"text","text":"deject vt. 使沮丧"},{"type":"entry","text":"erupt /ɪˈrʌpt/ vi. 喷出（熔岩、水、气体、泥浆等）","headword":"erupt"},{"type":"text","text":"eruption n. 火山爆发，喷发"},{"type":"entry","text":"outburst /ˈaʊtbɜːrst/ n. （火山等的）爆发","headword":"outburst"},{"type":"entry","text":"caldera /kælˈdera/ n. 破火山口（一种巨大的碗口形火山凹地）","headword":"caldera"}]},{"number":396,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"char /tʃɑːr/ v. 烧焦","headword":"char"},{"type":"text","text":"与“地震”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"seismic /ˈsaɪzmɪk/ a. 地震的","headword":"seismic"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 seism（震动）+ic→地震的"},{"type":"text","text":"seismic wave 地震波"},{"type":"text","text":"seismic focus 震源"},{"type":"text","text":"focal depth震源深度"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 epicentral intensity震源深度"},{"type":"entry","text":"epicenter /ˈepɪsentər/ n. 震中","headword":"epicenter"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 epi（在周围）＋center（中心）→震中"},{"type":"entry","text":"mainshock /meɪnʃɑːk/ n. 主震","headword":"mainshock"},{"type":"entry","text":"seismogram /ˈsaɪzməɡræm/ n. 地震图","headword":"seismogram"},{"type":"entry","text":"shake /ʃeɪk/ v./n. 震动；摇晃","headword":"shake"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 shake off摆脱"}]},{"number":397,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"shake up震动"},{"type":"e